div.p: This page provides a list of the FHIR artifacts defined as part of this implementation guide.
Profiles to be supported by EHRs and payor systems conforming to this implementation guide

tr.td: The Task resource is used to allow users to generate requests for information during the flow of DTR
The Questionnaire resource is used to represent the information needs that a payer has to satisfy their documentation requirements and/or rules
The QuestionnaireResponse resource is used to represent the information supplied by the provider
